description_fr:
{{Infobox/Jutsu|game names=Body Flicker Technique: Flame Slash|game debut=Naruto Mobile|jutsu media=Game|jutsu classification=Ninjutsu, Kenjutsu, Clone Techniques, Chakra Flow|jutsu type=Fire Release|jutsu class type=Offensive|jutsu range=Short|parent jutsu=Afterimage Clone, Body Flicker Technique, Uchiha Style: Dance of the Sun Halo|users=Shisui Uchiha}}
Shisui creates several afterimages, each of which attacks the opponent with a chakra-enhanced tantō, and finally Shisui himself, moving with lightning speed, finishes the attack by slicing through them with a fiery blade.
pl:Technika Błysku C

{{Infobox/Jutsu|game names=Explosion Release: Instantaneous Incineration|game debut=Naruto: Ultimate Ninja Online|jutsu media=Game|jutsu classification=Kekkei Genkai~Explosion Release, Ninjutsu|jutsu type=Explosion Release|jutsu class type=Offensive|jutsu range=Short|parent jutsu=Explosion Release: Landmine Fist|users=Gari}}
Gari concentrates the maximum explosive element in his fist, and when he strikes an opponent's body, it does not explode, but completely incinerates them in an instant.
pl:Uwolnienie Wybuchu: Natychmiastowe Spalanie

{{Infobox/Jutsu|game names=Heaven Gold|game debut=Naruto: Ultimate Ninja Online|jutsu media=Game|jutsu classification=Ninjutsu, Bukijutsu|jutsu class type=Offensive|jutsu range=Long|users=Fukurokumaru}}
Fukurokumaru lifts a gold bar into the air, causing huge gold bars to rain down on his opponents from the sky, injuring them.
pt-br:Ouro do Céu

{{Infobox/Jutsu|game names=Inuzuka Clan Glory|game debut=Naruto Mobile|jutsu media=Game|jutsu classification=Ninjutsu, Taijutsu, Chakra Flow, Cooperation Ninjutsu|jutsu class type=Offensive|jutsu range=Short|users=Hana Inuzuka~~with~Three Haimaru Brothers, Three Haimaru Brothers~~with~Hana Inuzuka}}
First, the Three Haimaru Brothers attack the enemy from different sides, moving very quickly, attacking with claws and teeth, after which Hana Inuzuka finishes him off with her sharp fingernails, enhanced with chakra, which is accompanied by bright red flashes.
pl:Sława Klanu Inuzuka

{{Infobox/Jutsu|game debut=Naruto Mobile|jutsu media=Anime, Game|jutsu classification=Ninjutsu|jutsu class type=Offensive|jutsu range=Short|parent jutsu=Car Mode|users=Mecha-Naruto}}
While in vehicle mode, Mecha-Naruto releases blades from his arms and head, which rotate at high speeds, cutting through anything in their path. The blades are powerful enough to easily slice through thick trees and the snakes summoned by Orochimaru. If necessary, the blades can be thrown at an escaping opponent, and they will pursue them, continuing to rotate at high speeds.
pt-br:Asas Mecânicas

{{Infobox/Jutsu|kanji=多重影分身の術 • 雷切|name-romaji=Tajū Kage Bunshin no Jutsu: Raikiri|game debut=Naruto Mobile|jutsu media=Game|jutsu classification=Kinjutsu, Ninjutsu, Clone Techniques|jutsu type=Lightning Release|jutsu class type=Offensive|jutsu range=Short|parent jutsu=Lightning Cutter, Multiple Shadow Clone Technique|users=Kakashi Hatake}}
Kakashi creates multiple shadow clones, each of which attacks the enemy using Lightning Cutter, after which Kakashi himself, using an enhanced version of Lightning Cutter, finishes off the enemy.
pl:Tajū Kage Bunshin no Jutsu: Raikiri

{{Infobox/Jutsu|game names=Raging Pounce|game debut=Naruto Mobile|jutsu media=Game|jutsu classification=Ninjutsu, Taijutsu, Cooperation Ninjutsu|jutsu class type=Offensive|jutsu range=Short|parent jutsu=Summoning Technique|users=Hana Inuzuka~~with~Three Haimaru Brothers, Three Haimaru Brothers~~with~Hana Inuzuka}}
Hana attacks her opponent with rapid strikes, slicing them with her sharp claws. A more powerful version of this technique allows Hana to summon the Three Haimaru Brothers, who fall upon the opponent from above, pinning them to the ground before tearing them with their fangs.
pl:Wści

{{Infobox/Jutsu|game names=Secret Sword: Flowing Shadow|game debut=Naruto Mobile|jutsu media=Game|jutsu classification=Ninjutsu, Clone Techniques, Kenjutsu|jutsu class type=Offensive|jutsu range=Short|parent jutsu=Shadow Clone Technique, Transparent Escape Technique|users=Hayate Gekkō}}
Hayate creates several shadow clones that attack the enemy with their swords. During this time, he himself becomes invisible, allowing him to launch a surprise attack at the right moment, even if the clones are destroyed.
pl:Tajemny Miecz: Płynący Cień

{{Infobox/Jutsu|game names=Uchiha Style: Four Directions Slash|game debut=Naruto Mobile|jutsu media=Game|jutsu classification=Ninjutsu, Kenjutsu, Chakra Flow|jutsu type=Fire Release|jutsu class type=Offensive|jutsu range=Mid|parent jutsu=Body Flicker Technique, Uchiha Style: Dance of the Sun Halo|users=Shisui Uchiha}}
Shisui powers up his tantō with Fire Release and, using the Body Flicker Technique, attacks the enemy from four sides, burning them with a fiery blade.
pl:Styl Uchihy: Cięcie w Czterech Kierunkach
